channel.title: How do i change the bonuses, i wanna make d great axe 150 str bonus
channel.description: Yes how do i change that. I'd like to know, i want the great axe to own.

item.title: How do i change the bonuses, i wanna make d great axe 150 str bonus
item.dc:creator: @Sick_of_Air Sick of Air
item.description:
@Sick_of_Air wrote:

Open up items.cfg and search for the great axe, you should see:

[code]item = 4718 Dharoks_greataxe Dharok_the_Wretched’s_greataxe. 124256.3840357 3940886.69950738 166082.987535763 -4 103 95 -4 0 0 0 0 0 -1 105 0[/code

The first 3 numbers, don’t touch them, those are the prices. The last 12 numbers are the bonuses. Change them and then compile.[/code]
